# NFPA Permit System Demo: End-to-End Permit Lifecycle

## Scenario: Commercial Building Fire Alarm System Installation

### 1. Initial Application
**Applicant: John Smith (ABC Electrical)**
- Project: Fire Alarm System Installation
- Location: 123 Main St, Suite 100
- Building Type: Commercial Office
- Square Footage: 5,000 sq ft

**Documents Uploaded:**
- Floor plans (PDF, 2.5MB)
- Fire alarm system specifications (PDF, 1.8MB)
- NFPA 72 compliance documentation (PDF, 3.2MB)
- Electrical load calculations (PDF, 1.5MB)

**AI Analysis Results:**
- NFPA 72 Compliance: 92%
- Missing Requirements:
  - Battery backup specifications
  - Emergency power supply details
- Recommendations:
  - Add battery backup documentation
  - Include emergency power supply specifications
  - Update floor plans with device locations

### 2. Inspector Review
**Inspector: Sarah Johnson (Fire Marshal's Office)**
- Initial Review: 2024-03-15 10:30 AM
- Comments:
  - "Please provide battery backup specifications"
  - "Emergency power supply details required"
  - "Update floor plans with device locations"
- Status: Revision Required

### 3. Applicant Response
**Additional Documents Uploaded:**
- Battery backup specifications (PDF, 1.2MB)
- Emergency power supply details (PDF, 1.5MB)
- Updated floor plans (PDF, 2.8MB)

**AI Analysis Results:**
- NFPA 72 Compliance: 98%
- All requirements met
- No additional recommendations

### 4. Final Review
**Inspector: Sarah Johnson**
- Final Review: 2024-03-16 2:15 PM
- Comments:
  - "All requirements met"
  - "Documentation complete"
  - "System design compliant"
- Status: Approved

### 5. Permit Issuance
**System Actions:**
- Generate permit document
- Create blockchain record
- Send approval notifications
- Update permit status

**Blockchain Transaction:**
- Transaction ID: 0x1234...5678
- Timestamp: 2024-03-16 2:20 PM
- Hash: 0xabcd...efgh
- Status: Confirmed

### 6. Post-Issuance
**System Updates:**
- Permit added to dashboard
- Audit log updated
- Notifications sent
- Reports generated

**Available Actions:**
- View permit details
- Download permit document
- Check blockchain verification
- Generate compliance report

